{"tid":1024431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那污染物又消耗香港醫療資源","createTime":"2019-02-16T14:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T05:31:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78351ded445ee36c131a14e35c93fc56bfbf06fc","tid":1024431,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10161408053800207&amp;set=p.10161408053800207&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10161408053800207%26set%3Dp.10161408053800207%26type%3D3%26theater&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=897d6b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10161408053800207&amp;set=p.10161408053800207&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/52422217_10161408053805207_7548731405874757632_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6bba3bc2013cf655f4164a6a7584e250&amp;oe=5D262EB0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F52422217_10161408053805207_7548731405874757632_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D6bba3bc2013cf655f4164a6a7584e250%26oe%3D5D262EB0&h=28110b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHot topic 真係話口未完<br />\n<br />\n話說尋晚on call 收咗個80幾歲阿婆<br />\n阿婆本身住喺大陸，啱啱一個月之前攞到香港身分證，不過其實都仲住緊係大陸。<br />\n幾日前喺大陸屋企跌親，去埋大陸醫院照埋電腦掃描見到斷骨。明明大灣區先係人類嘅伊甸園，但係又要帶阿婆返嚟香港呢啲第三世界醫。🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n好啦行埋牀邊做檢查，阿婆唔識聽唔識講廣東話都預咗啦，大佬原來普通話都唔識聽唔識講。問吓床邊四個屋企人，四個都用啲唔鹹唔淡嘅廣東話答我，話阿婆自己長期買血壓藥食但係冇任何複診。<br />\n術前檢查係要照肺嘅。一打開阿婆張肺片睇，「心胸廣闊」已經唔足夠形容阿婆個心有幾大，好明顯係長期心臟有問題冇處理過。不過其實就算佢好健康都冇得即刻做手術，因為而家緊急手術條隊排到星期一都未做得完。😪<br />\n<br />\n結論：照肺check心做手術駁骨物理治療開藥複診，120蚊一日真係抵到爛，各位唔買都埋黎睇睇🎊🎉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#如有雷同實屬不幸<br />\n#個ward爆到fracturehip都要瞓街床<br />\n#家庭團聚<br />\n#好似就嚟又要交稅<br />\n#彭生問你數據呢？<br />\n#冇數據我哋好難討論喎<br />\n#大家一齊估下阿婆住公屋定私樓?<br />\n#又再估吓做完手術會唔會申請傷殘津貼?<br />\n#中港一家人<br />\n#生係中國人死係HA鬼<br />\n#竭誠為大灣區同胞服務<br />\n<br />\n[圖文不符] 同場加映有另一個阿婆吞左個兩蚊同隻戒指👻<br />\n&mdash; at Caritas Medical Centre."},{"pid":"aacfe0d81c2b4f096cd8ada286e12a43c35f4016","tid":1024431,"uid":69013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:27:20.000Z","msg":"我自己遇過 一個雙目失明，50-60歲女人， 全講普通話；另一個截左2雙小腿既男人，都係50-60歲，又係淨識普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n次次諗交咁多稅比呢班前半生對香港完全無貢獻既人（後半生應該都唔會有），就會好嬲。 佢地仲可以一排公屋即有得住。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcccf86db400ff999bbfa83c008ae0ee590ec013","tid":1024431,"uid":24730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"喉嚨有個兩蚊銀塞住？"},{"pid":"7de5365712d1701f15925593a188505f386b81ec","tid":1024431,"uid":13490,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"同埋好撚多支那狗喺支那醫唔掂就過黎<br />\n個個拎著深圳人民醫院啲xray片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a9ef6f66d01db1b60acdd61ffe43ed72ba09fd","tid":1024431,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b4213c6058c79174144ecc79b6feaba74c6255c0","tid":1024431,"uid":19287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:11:26.000Z","msg":"80幾歲阿婆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係香港先咁on9唔洗驗身同比咁大年紀既人移民黎"},{"pid":"819712b54e05635572ca21653614eb225f93e0eb","tid":1024431,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fccced73da04a41a4acc1d5542d1f6e6d31c54b","tid":1024431,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T02:22:17.000Z","msg":"點解吞完戒指吞兩蚊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我當佢隻戒指係意外跌咗落食物，兩蚊咁大好難係意外喎<br />\n<br />\n我估佢想用兩蚊推隻戒指快啲痾返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e88314ac8d74635166d2d86d6bb8c0190dee5e","tid":1024431,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"08f070a0f6d0367f182d52ef92d38cf16d2fd7c5","tid":1024431,"uid":135475,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"啲hashtags做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe50f9a7c150bc0c8321b2bcc5bae7ceee674521","tid":1024431,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}